Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,UWP 声音版 —— 使用 MediaElement 控件播放声音\N\N翻译 : scripter糖　审核：@geelaw（微博）　压制：<压制人>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.67,0:00:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so now it's time to have fun./好了，现在就是娱乐时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.29,0:00:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to actually wire up the/我们用 MediaElement 来播放音频
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.66,0:00:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll also do a little clean up and get the filtering to work/我也会做一些筛选的功能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.19,0:00:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,by selecting one of the categories./通过选择其中一种分类
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.40,0:00:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Only show those categories in the GridView./从而在GridView中只显示此类别音频
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.14,0:00:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's go ahead and get started here.//那就从这里开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.74,0:00:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to open up the MainPage.xaml/我现在去打开MainPage.xaml
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and in here what I want to do is handle the,/在这里我想处理一下，嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.86,0:00:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this is it, the ListView_ItemClick Event./我想可能是它， ListView_ItemClick事件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.12,0:00:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me make sure that's the correct EventHandler./让我们搞清楚这是否是正确的事件处理方法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.03,0:00:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So basically when somebody selects/当某人选择了SoundGridView中的某一个Item
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.45,0:00:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,that we created, we want to play the sound/对应的音频需要被播放
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.24,0:00:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that's associated with the image that was clicked on./那也意味着某一张图片被点击过了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.12,0:00:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So, actually, this is the EventHandler that we want./所以呢，这应该就是我们需要的事件处理方法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.90,0:00:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,SoundGridView_ItemClick./SoundGridView_ItemClick
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.34,0:00:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们继续
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.52,0:01:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这个方法我们已经不再需要它了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If we do, we'll add it back./如果以后还要用就把它再加回来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.35,0:01:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, and so here it's pretty easy stuff./好，现在这里看起来就很简单了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.13,0:01:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All we need to do is grab the Item that was clicked on/我们只需要分清楚被点击具体的的Item
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.35,0:01:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and so that'll be given to us here/那么这里给了我们一个参数 ItemClickEventArgs e
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.52,0:01:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And we can just choose the clicked Item and then/然后我们选择 ClickedItem 之后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.25,0:01:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,cast that to what it represents/把它的类型转换为它实际的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.90,0:01:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,which is a sound in our application./也就是我们应用中的 Sound
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.26,0:01:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can do something like this:/所以我又 var 了一个变量 sound，对应的就是音频
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we'll set, I think I called it/接下来我们设置一些属性，应该是 MyMediaElement.Source
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.20,0:01:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,MyMediaElement.Source, and we'll just set it to/我们把它设置成对应的音频文件属性
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.77,0:01:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, to do this, we actually need to give it a URI,/为了做到这个，我们需要一个 Uri
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.46,0:01:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,if you hover over, you can see the Source property/当鼠标停在上面，你可以看见对应的Source属性
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.53,0:01:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,accepts a URI, which is a Uniform Resource Indicator,/接受一个URI  \N （URI : Uniform Resource Indicator，统一资源指示符）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.89,0:01:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's just going to be a location for the file./这也就是表示文件所处的地址
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.54,0:01:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what we need to do, there's a couple/我们现在有很多种方案来填写参数
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the easiest way is just to specify the base URI./我认为最简单的就是设置 baseUri
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.35,0:02:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That will give us, like, the root of the project,/这会给予我们一个好用的东西，像是这个项目的起点一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.11,0:02:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we can give it the actual audio file/然后我们就需要给予它实际的音频文件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.45,0:02:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,that will contain that /Assets/Audio/Category/Sound./这会包含 “/Assets/Audio/Category/Sound”路径下的文件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.63,0:02:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll just do this.BaseUri,/我们选择 this.BaseUri
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we'll use the sound.AudioFile/接下来就是使用 sound.AudioFile
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.46,0:02:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and, with any luck, this will actually work,/嗯，运气不错的话，就应该就可以管用了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.75,0:02:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,so let's see what we've got so far./那就让我们看看做了这么多所收获的成果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, it's time for the moment of truth./现在就是揭晓真相的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.18,0:02:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,(laugh)/（笑声）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.06,0:02:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,(siren)/（汽笛声）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:02:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,(cow moos)/（牛的声音）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.77,0:02:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, so it was that easy./好了，就是这么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.18,0:03:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all we needed to do to wire everything up, great./这就是我们连接所有东西所需要做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, when we ran the application,/现在，当我们运行这个程序的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.76,0:03:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,there were some other issues with layout,/还有一些关于界面布局的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,with the hamburger navigation,/比如汉堡按钮导航
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,let's go ahead and fix some of those things,/让我们继续修正并解决它们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.86,0:03:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,because that's really what's holding us back now./因为这真的有必要再回顾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me take note of a few things,/我们会记录下需要修正的事项
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,rerunning the application here,/现在返回到这个应用中来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'll just address them little by little./我们会一点点的解决
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.31,0:03:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so you can see here that we've got some/好，的确是有问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,issues with each of the ListView Items./ListView 的项显示并不完全
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the text needs to be moved down a little bit./标题文字需要往下放一点，从而居中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can move things to the left a bit,/如果我们把它们整体往左边移动一下就很有帮助了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.16,0:03:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that would be helpful, because we wanted to line up/因为我们很需要把这些项对齐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, generally, some spacing issues there./另外一个问题看起来就是空间问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.29,0:03:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,As far as these items, they need to be/这些项需要被往左边移动一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.15,0:03:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's just it's just kind of running together here,/因为看起来就像是挤在一起了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.84,0:03:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,in that upper left-hand corner area./在左上角的区域
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.40,0:03:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's work on those two things right now./来着手为这两者开工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go over to the the MainPage.xaml./现在来查看 MainPage.xaml 文件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.66,0:04:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, as far as the MediaElement is concerned,/现在我们最关注的 MediaElement
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.41,0:04:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,we're going to use it at length for another project,/它的更多功能将在其它项目中被使用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and we're going to learn how to manipulate the sounds,/比如我们将会学习如何操作音频文件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.69,0:04:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and how much of the sound to play,/以及播放音量的控制
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.49,0:04:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,how do we manipulate the volume so that it/怎么使它们播放结束的时候渐渐淡去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,nicely fades out, instead of abruptly ends./而不是戛然而止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,When we get to another project/当我们到另外一个项目的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.81,0:04:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that we're going to work on together,/就是全部运用的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,so this is really our introduction to the MediaElement./所以这是我们真正的 MediaElement 的初学引导
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It can also play videos,/它也能播放视频
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.49,0:04:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,which I don't think we're going to demonstrate/我想我们不需要在这个版本里证明了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.84,0:04:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,in this series, but if you take a look/如果你有看过我为 Windows 8.1 以及 Windows Phone 8.1 做的开发指导视频
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,video, using the MediaElement./就知道我演示过怎么使用 MediaElement 播放视频
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.18,0:04:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok, so let's go up here to ListView,/现在上来看看 ListView
