Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.06,0:05:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see what kind of impact that has./来看看这些修改的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.59,0:05:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, that definitely moved things over to the left,/很好，它们已经移动到了左边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.36,0:06:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,which is great, and it looks like we've centered the text./真是太好了，这些字体看起来也被垂直居中了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.41,0:06:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good too. And the last thing,/最后一件事.....
